# Super Netball Leading Goalscorer Award

The Super Netball Leading Goalscorer Award is an annual Super Netball award given to the player that scores the most goals in the Super Netball regular season (not including finals matches). The current holder of the award is Jhaniele Fowler-Nembhard, who has led the competition in scoring for the past eight seasons.
